{"title":"献给孩子们的歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给孩子们的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来的世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关登瀛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们种的小树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴着春天的雨露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同我们放飞的白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我们呼唤和平的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里没有战争的硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有饥饿的眼泪和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙伴的恸哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是世界新一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽在一起的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分肤色不分种族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来是我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让友谊与和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着我们成长、进步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花鹿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张俊以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花鹿身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵朵梅花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁种的呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁施的肥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁浇的水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不怎么开得这样大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种花的阿姨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在哪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我多想找到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉我的海军衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知还用不用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉小裤衩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好阿姨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求您把梅花种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我身上种下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也一定能开遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的梅花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到那时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就变成小鹿啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要蹦蹦跳跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑进迷人的大森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和小猴跳舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听小鸟唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪小熊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说说心里话……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东走在春天的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东七岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只黄狗与一只白鹅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一起读拼音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呜、呜、呜”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咯、咯、咯”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校预备的钟声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东想起在讲台上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女老师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的教鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是春天的一根手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手指有多高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天就有多高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸一摸书包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书包里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个生字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她怕生字跑掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天晚上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在油灯下把生字捉住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东要拿给老师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东东看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一个足球，腾地一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被谁踢了出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个学校和星期一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被映成了红的……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女老师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也成了红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进童年的森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光是我最好的朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风儿向着我热情地打着招呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树叶儿“哗哗”的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有雨点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个不速之客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄地沐浴着树枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄地浸湿着我的面庞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿时的伙伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都已不见了踪影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有几棵古树刻下的誓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在讲述着亘古不变的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有童年捡拾的蘑菇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知趣地一个个露出了白花花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诱惑着我放慢脚步"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}